editTeamScoresDescription: Tap the check mark to reset all team scores. Choose a number from 1 to 9999.
resetPassSuccessMessageText: A link to reset your password was sent to your email.
accountDeletionErrorText: Please try to login again. If able to do so, your account was NOT deleted. Retry account deletion to finalize.
logoutMessage: LOGOUT then LOGIN to delete account!
editRetoDescription: ‘RETO’ is a Spanish word for ‘challenge’. Specify a challenge for the losing teams to perform after one team wins the game.

rules.ruleDescription: Any of your team members may claim the challenge points. Multiple team members may attempt to complete the challenge at the same time.
There is no limit to the number of players per team.
Only one team can claim points for a challenge. If there's a tie, decide on a tie breaker.
